## Production Deployment Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant CLI as Smart Deploy CLI
    participant Orch as Production Orchestrator
    participant Val as Enhanced Validator
    participant BG as Blue-Green Manager
    participant Mon as Production Monitor
    participant Git as Git Expert
    participant FB as Firebase Production
    participant Stake as Stakeholders
    
    Dev->>CLI: ./smart-deploy.sh --production
    CLI->>Orch: Initialize Production Deployment
    
    Orch->>Val: Enhanced Production Validation
    Val->>Val: Security Scan
    Val->>Val: Compliance Check
    Val->>Val: Performance Baseline
    Val->>Orch: Validation Complete ✓
    
    Orch->>Git: Create Release Tag
    Git->>Git: Semantic Versioning
    Git->>Git: Generate Release Notes
    Git->>Orch: Version Tagged ✓
    
    Orch->>BG: Initialize Blue-Green Deploy
    BG->>FB: Deploy to Green Environment
    FB->>BG: Green Deployment Complete
    
    BG->>Mon: Start Canary Testing
    Mon->>Mon: Health Checks (5 min)
    Mon->>Mon: Performance Validation
    Mon->>BG: Canary Success ✓
    
    BG->>FB: Switch Traffic to Green
    FB->>BG: Traffic Switch Complete
    BG->>FB: Mark Blue as Standby
    
    Mon->>Mon: Continuous Monitoring
    Mon->>Stake: Success Notification
    
    Note over Dev,Stake: Zero-downtime deployment complete!
    
    %% Rollback Scenario
    alt Production Issue Detected
        Mon->>BG: Trigger Automatic Rollback
        BG->>FB: Switch Traffic to Blue
        FB->>BG: Rollback Complete
        BG->>Stake: Rollback Notification
    end
